ming a community group or participating in a class. A host and plenty of staff members and volunteers will be on hand to navigate you through the process of meeting others and connecting for growth.&nbsp;GroupLink is a great way to get connected!</p><p>Light snacks will be provided.</p><p><video width="370" height="250" preload="none" controls="controls" src="http://f049e6c6bc51d6086828-1f3d9bf827f6f62072870f1ea348709c.r40.cf2.rackcdn.com/h264-720/v/0e2426267_1377728136_video--grouplink-promo-video.mp4"><object width="370" height="250" data="/vendor/tinymce/plugins/media/moxieplayer.swf" type="application/x-shockwave-flash"><param name="src" value="/vendor/tinymce/plugins/media/moxieplayer.swf"><param name="play" value="false"><param name="quality" value="autohigh"><param name="flashvars" value="url=http%3A//f049e6c6bc51d6086828-1f3d9bf827f6f62072870f1ea348709c.r40.cf2.rackcdn.com/h264-720/v/0e2426267_1377728136_video--grouplink-promo-video.mp4&amp;poster=/Page/edit/418341/"><param name="allowfullscreen" value="true"><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="true"><param name="autoplay" value="false"><param name="scale" value="aspect"></object></video></p><p><a href="https://secure.accessacs.com/access/eventlogin.aspx?id=vGihGhslbOLuQ2lOa0BerQ==&amp;site=1233&amp;ReturnUrl=events%2fwz_people.aspx&amp;ChurchID=3183&amp;EventID=51351&amp;sn=1233" class="button">Register Here</a></p><hr><h3><img src="http://www.pcctoday.com/monkimage.php?mediaDirectory=mediafiles&amp;mediaId=2277801&amp;fileName=graphic--staff-photo--joel-slater-crop-0-0-150-210.jpg" width="150" height="210" alt="GRAPHIC : STAFF PHOTO : Joel Slater - Crop" title="GRAPHIC : STAFF PHOTO : Joel Slater - Crop" style="float: left; margin: 0px 20px 10px 0;">Pastoral Oversight</h3><p class="class-intstructor-bio"><strong>PASTOR JOEL SLATER</strong>&nbsp;serves as Congregational Life Pastor at Portland Christian Center which includes oversight of the small groups ministry.</p><p class="class-intstructor-bio">Having grown up in this church, Joel is a product of the intentional, consistent discipleship offered here. &nbsp;An ordained minister, Joel has served in various roles ranging from children to youth to adult ministries for the last 14 years, 8 of those at Portland Christian Center. &nbsp;Throughout that time, Joel has experienced an ever-growing love for Jesus and realization that understanding the centrality of Jesus makes the Christian life truly genuine and powerful. &nbsp;Joel is married to Amy Slater, and together they are raising 3 children, Sydney, Brooklyn, and Jackson. &nbsp;</p><p>Follow/Contact Pastor Joel Slater: <a href="http://www.facebook.com/joel.d.slater" class="facebook" target="_blank">Facebook</a> <a href="http://twitter.com/pastorjoels" class="twitter" target="_blank">Twitter</a> <a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=84258767&amp;locale=en_US&amp;trk=tyah" class="linkedin" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a> <a href="mailto:jslater@pcctoday.com" class="email" target="_blank">Email</a></p>